Class GUILevelDisplayer

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.scene.Node
      • javafx.scene.canvas.Canvas
        • view.GUILevelDisplayer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.css.Styleable, javafx.event.EventTarget

    public class GUILevelDisplayer
extends javafx.scene.canvas.Canvas
    This class displays images to the screen using JavaFx's Canvas class. Images are uploaded to the program via FXML.
    Author:
    Or Priesender
